---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs WiserNotify — Social Proof Tool Comparison | SocialProof" description="WiserNotify starts at $16/mo and focuses on notification popups. SocialProof is free to start and $9/mo Pro — built for testimonial widgets, not conversion tricks." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/wisernotify">
<style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: .45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .vs-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f0f0f0; color: #555; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: .35rem .75rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #4f46e5; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #444; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .hero-cta:hover { background: #3730a3; }
    .price-callout { display: inline-flex; gap: 2rem; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .price-callout .item { text-align: center; }
    .price-callout .item .price { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .price-callout .item .label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #777; margin-top: .2rem; }
    .price-callout .item.vouch .price { color: #4f46e5; }
    .price-callout .item.other .price { color: #dc2626; }
    section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .compare-table th { padding: .75rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; color: #888; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; }
    .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { color: #4f46e5; }
    .compare-table td { padding: .85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 0.97rem; vertical-align: top; }
    .compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .compare-table td:first-child { color: #555; font-weight: 500; }
    .yes { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .no { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; }
    .partial { color: #d97706; font-weight: 600; }
    .winner-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .winner-card { border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem; }
    .winner-card.vouch { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #86efac; }
    .winner-card.other { background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; }
    .winner-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 .75rem; }
    .winner-card ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; }
    .winner-card li { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #444; margin-bottom: .4rem; }
    .savings-box { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; text-align: center; }
    .savings-box strong { font-size: 1.2rem; }
    .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; padding: 1.25rem 0; }
    .faq-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .faq-item h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .5rem; }
    .faq-item p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; margin: 0; }
    .cta-section { text-align: center; background: #f5f3ff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 3rem 2rem; margin: 3rem 0; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .cta-section p { color: #555; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; color: #999; font-size: 0.85rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    footer a { color: #999; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 .75rem; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .price-callout { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; } .winner-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
<nav>
    <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/vs/">Comparisons</a>
        <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev" class="cta-nav">Try Free</a>
    </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
    <span class="vs-badge">SocialProof vs WiserNotify</span>
    <h1>WiserNotify uses <span>popups &amp; pressure</span>.<br>SocialProof builds real trust.</h1>
    <p>WiserNotify is a conversion notification tool that flashes "Sarah from Chicago just bought!" popups. SocialProof embeds your actual customer testimonials — real words from real people who love you.</p>
    <div class="price-callout">
        <div class="item vouch">
            <div class="price">Free</div>
            <div class="label">SocialProof — free forever for 1 widget</div>
        </div>
        <div class="item other">
            <div class="price">$16/mo</div>
            <div class="label">WiserNotify — entry plan, limited pageviews</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev" class="hero-cta">Start free with SocialProof →</a>
</div>

<section>
    <h2>What each tool actually does</h2>
    <p>These are fundamentally different products. <strong>WiserNotify</strong> shows small notification popups in the corner of your site — "X people are viewing this," "Someone just signed up" — designed to create urgency and FOMO. <strong>SocialProof</strong> collects testimonials from your real customers and displays them in a clean embeddable widget. One manufactures pressure; the other surfaces genuine advocacy.</p>

    <table class="compare-table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Feature</th>
                <th>SocialProof</th>
                <th>WiserNotify</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>Core function</td>
                <td class="yes">Collect &amp; display real testimonials</td>
                <td>FOMO notification popups</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Free plan</td>
                <td class="yes">Free forever for 1 active widget</td>
                <td class="no">14-day trial only</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Testimonial collection forms</td>
                <td class="yes">Built in — text &amp; star ratings</td>
                <td class="no">Not the focus</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Embeddable widget</td>
                <td class="yes">Yes — copy one line of code</td>
                <td class="partial">Popup only, not embeddable inline</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Real customer quotes displayed</td>
                <td class="yes">Yes — your actual reviews</td>
                <td class="no">Activity notifications, not testimonials</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Review moderation / approval</td>
                <td class="yes">Full control over what shows</td>
                <td class="partial">Limited</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Setup time</td>
                <td class="yes">Under 5 minutes</td>
                <td class="partial">Longer — many notification types to configure</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Looks like spam / fake urgency</td>
                <td class="yes">No — just honest reviews</td>
                <td class="no">Can feel gimmicky to savvy shoppers</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Works for service businesses</td>
                <td class="yes">Built for them</td>
                <td class="partial">Better suited for e-commerce</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Starting price</td>
                <td class="yes">Free forever / $9/mo Pro</td>
                <td class="no">$16/mo minimum</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>The notification popup debate</h2>
    <p>There's an honest conversation happening in the conversion optimization world about FOMO notification tools. The popups work — in the short term. But they have real downsides that WiserNotify won't mention on their pricing page:</p>
    <div class="winner-grid">
        <div class="winner-card vouch">
            <h3>Why testimonials win long-term</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Build trust, not just urgency</li>
                <li>No "fake vibes" — modern buyers are skeptical of activity popups</li>
                <li>Work for service businesses where volume is low</li>
                <li>Help SEO — testimonial content is real content</li>
                <li>Customers feel honored to be featured</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="winner-card other">
            <h3>WiserNotify's limitations</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Requires pageview volume to look credible</li>
                <li>Small service businesses can't fake "73 people viewing"</li>
                <li>Ad blockers often block notification scripts</li>
                <li>Can feel manipulative — may hurt conversion with informed buyers</li>
                <li>Ongoing monthly cost with no free tier</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="savings-box">
        <strong>Switch from WiserNotify and save $192/year</strong><br>
        SocialProof Pro is $9/mo. WiserNotify's entry plan is $16/mo. That's $84/year saved — plus SocialProof is built for the job you actually need.
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Who should use each</h2>
    <p><strong>Use WiserNotify if:</strong> You run a high-volume e-commerce store and want urgency-driven conversion popups alongside a suite of other social proof notifications. You have 10K+ monthly visitors and the numbers will look credible.</p>
    <p><strong>Use SocialProof if:</strong> You're a small business, service provider, freelancer, or early-stage SaaS that wants to display genuine customer testimonials. You want something honest, embeddable, and free to start.</p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can SocialProof show activity notifications like WiserNotify?</h3>
        <p>No — and that's intentional. SocialProof focuses on collecting and displaying real testimonials from your customers. Activity notifications ("5 people viewing") are a different category of tool. We believe authentic reviews build more durable trust than urgency tactics.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Is SocialProof really free forever?</h3>
        <p>Yes. One active widget, unlimited testimonials, free forever. No credit card required to start. Upgrade to Pro ($9/mo) to unlock multiple widgets, custom branding removal, and priority support.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Does SocialProof work if I don't have many customers yet?</h3>
        <p>Absolutely. Even 3–5 testimonials displayed well can dramatically increase conversions. You don't need hundreds of reviews. You need the right ones, displayed at the right moment.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can I migrate my reviews from WiserNotify?</h3>
        <p>If you have testimonials collected in WiserNotify or anywhere else, you can add them manually to SocialProof in minutes. Our collection forms make it easy to gather new ones going forward.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="cta-section" style="max-width:900px; margin: 0 auto 3rem;">
    <h2>Real testimonials beat fake urgency</h2>
    <p>Start collecting and displaying genuine customer reviews today — free forever for 1 widget.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev" class="hero-cta">Try SocialProof free →</a>
</div>

<footer>
    <a href="/">SocialProof</a>
    <a href="/vs/">All Comparisons</a>
    <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev">Sign Up Free</a>
    <br><br>© 2025 SocialProof. All rights reserved.
</footer>

<div class="footer-links" style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:0.9rem;">
